cdse_client.pl — Perl CLI Client
==================================

Perl 5 command-line client for the CaumeDSE REST API.  Supports encrypted
secret storage, encrypted CSV databases, user/org info, and the audit log.
Runs in one-shot mode (single command per invocation) or in an interactive
REPL.


CONTENTS
========
